This repository contains original artistic, academic, musical, technical, and multimedia work, 
including Pure Data patches, documentation, system designs, research materials, musical scores, 
and related content developed as part of the doctoral research project:

“Diseño y Desarrollo de Sistemas MMHCI Híbridos con Bioseñales y un DMI de Smartphones para 
Obras Bio-Interactivas Mixtas y Performáticas”.

